OL,4,CUniversal credit claimants must seek
OL,5,C18 hours work
OL,6,GPeople claiming universal credit and
OL,7,Gworking fewer than 18 hours a week
OL,8,Gwill be expected to look for more
OL,9,Gwork, after a change to the welfare
OL,10,Gsystem that starts on Monday.
OL,12,FBefore now, claimants only had to work
OL,13,F15 hours.
OL,15,FThe new rule is part of broader
OL,16,Freforms to the welfare system that the
OL,17,Fgovernment announced last month.
OL,19,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,20,Fsaid the rule change meant 180,000
OL,21,Fpeople would have to work more.
